  "detailed_description": "Slime Jumper Adventure is an adventure platform game, where you play as Mr. Slime who must traverse through forests, caves, skies and even space in order to reunite with his family. make your way through countless traps and obstacles like spikes, lasers, projectiles and even aliens as Mr. Slime across 5 unique worlds with numerous levels. Reaching the goal at the end of each level is key to progressing to the next stage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010220/extras/3a8a38927b4d8621f37c7f9cbb65b701.poster.avif?t=1703811906\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010220/extras/3a8a38927b4d8621f37c7f9cbb65b701.webm?t=1703811906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010220/extras/3a8a38927b4d8621f37c7f9cbb65b701.mp4?t=1703811906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Game Components</strong><br>- Over 25 Unique Levels.<br>- 5 Different World.<br>- Travers Traps & Obstacles.<br>- Puzzle Platformer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010220/extras/148ef0cbe9876d32ce2cf94ac3c28cc5.poster.avif?t=1703811906\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010220/extras/148ef0cbe9876d32ce2cf94ac3c28cc5.webm?t=1703811906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2010220/extras/148ef0cbe9876d32ce2cf94ac3c28cc5.mp4?t=1703811906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Challenges</strong><br>- Spikes.<br>- Lasers.<br>- Projectiles.<br>- Aliens.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_im